{
  "stem": "23428.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But that was just to cover up their own safety.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was-- they were very magnanimous in taking us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And at one point or another, we also had German passports, Fascist passports, which again has to do with this Aryanization process, because at one point or another, I think the German embassy in Budapest took the attitude that as long as this process was not decided, they would-- they would give us German passports.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That also may have helped to keep us in that school.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But of course, it was-- OK.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as soon as we were in that school-- this is the same-- same sort of school that my children now visit in Washington.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Instead of having English taught in English, they had Hungarian and Hungarian history and Hungarian geography taught in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so when we entered the school, I remember memorizing pages and pages of text in Hungarian that we didn't really know, we didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we could spit it back and do our homework that way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was very hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then of course it was time we learned Hungarian, as kids do.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in fact, at the end, in 1944, I took my baccalaureate, both in Hungarian and in German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is the high school graduation, yeah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, school in Budapest was-- was-- was, again, a time of-- of really great peace.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were not harassed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were not harassed because the teachers, as I say, didn't harass us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were a little bit in a funny position, because all the Hungarian kids belonged to Hungarian youth organization .",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "All the German kids belonged to the Hitler Jugend.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't belong to anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
